            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A carbon target of thickness 240+-25 mu-g/cm2, obtained",
                "by evaporating carbon from a carbon arc onto a tungsten",
                "backing, was used for the experiment. It was mounted at",
                "45 degr. to the beam direction in a thin walled (2 mm",
                "thick) aluminium target chamber suspended over a",
                "rotating table, from which angles could be read to an",
                "accuracy of 0.5 degr."
